      void actionPerformed(java.awt.event.ActionEvent e)
      This is the ActionEvent handler for this class There are 3 possible kind of actions to be called : - Back, return to the root listView - Remove, will remove the selected plugin if the conditions are matched (not internal) - Add, will add a plugin if the type is right (ie. not adding a feature to the language) and if not already added This method is throwing a lot of exceptions and handle them by itself
